{"tid":2237824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"認真一問，lunch gor有冇幫手宣傳過德國聯署？","createTime":"2020-10-10T15:01:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T17:18:30.000Z","uid":200550,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1f77e71835503b78b0ce04f586b19fc0984dd21e","tid":2237824,"uid":200550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T15:01:40.000Z","msg":"［最後10日緊急要人！］德國聯署逐步圖文教學<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2237513\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2237513</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n講真你嗰啲咩露械/性騷擾女手足/玩汽水我冇咩留意<br />\n因為我唔會花咁多時間留意一個on9仔<br />\n但既然你自稱星級抗爭團隊，又起晒大台咁，你fb page都有2萬幾人follow, 點解你竟然連咁緊要嘅一個聯署都冇幫手推過？仲要呢個聯署係<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">有法律效力嘅，要擺上德國國會</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你咁得閒寫信畀林奠做筆友，日日出嚟做on9嘢，但你連出一個post都唔做？你到底係抗爭定出嚟seek attention? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />作為一個叫做有啲影響力嘅人可唔可以嘗試下好好利用你嘅影響力而唔係日日做on9嘢呢？"},{"pid":"cccece698c8e5ccb7b2797a5d4012cb36bec4169","tid":2237824,"uid":200550,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T15:09:00.000Z","msg":"跟住講嘅主要係發晦氣屌下李國永啲fans<br />\n唔想睇嘅就skip啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sDSMt3X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsDSMt3X.jpg&h=866034e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D1SHMQD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD1SHMQD.jpg&h=53909dfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌你老母呢班咁嘅撚樣仲垃圾過lunch gor<br />\n如果你地真係咁撐佢嘅咁點解每次佢<span class=\"red\">和你鳩</span>都係得一個人而唔係成個星級抗爭團隊出晒嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n說到底就係一班唔願付出唔願貢獻但係又抱住贖罪心態，覺得自己關注lunch gor就當抗爭咗，屌撚晒你地老母仲要當佢神咁拜。人地批評下你地就話人分化撚五毛，我明，你地唔想認lunch gor垃圾呀嘛，因為承認佢係垃圾即係承認自己都係垃撚圾，邊有人會自認垃圾啫？<br />\n呢個所謂星級抗爭團隊同邪教根本就冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5085a968aa65ee6ce72e7b09069f766b5b38504a","tid":2237824,"uid":200550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T15:09:20.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">簽名啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"b5425fe71774202d45d362971080a0b1eb2031a1","tid":2237824,"uid":200558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T15:10:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9640511b228b103a3cd9aadfc237e0771431295c","tid":2237824,"uid":200550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T15:10:36.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">簽名呀</span></span>"},{"pid":"8b2d82b3001482283e750038b1cda1785bfcddc1","tid":2237824,"uid":200558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T15:10:43.000Z","msg":"仲差兩萬人簽名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ad0089b24f73a3f88befe7a4fc1032ee4898e8","tid":2237824,"uid":200550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8b2d82b3001482283e750038b1cda1785bfcddc1","tid":2237824,"uid":200558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T15:10:43.000Z","msg":"仲差兩萬人簽名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T15:11:43.000Z","msg":"白宮啲濕鳩聯署就次次都簽爆<br />\n真係有用嘅就唔見人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同李國永一樣"},{"pid":"b67c62fa5ba2958ff2fdf163022bc28f5953b0c1","tid":2237824,"uid":200550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T15:11:59.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">簽名呀</span></span>"},{"pid":"97131eefb02f7bf9572e3e59f54ee1221012bb99","tid":2237824,"uid":200550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T15:12:40.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">簽名呀</span></span>"},{"pid":"3914e3c5e3fa6c3bacaf64e453fe88c5a4294da1","tid":2237824,"uid":200550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T15:13:10.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">簽名呀